import React from 'react'
  import { MDXTag } from '@mdx-js/tag'
  

export default class MDXContent extends React.Component {
  constructor(props) {
    super(props)
    this.layout = null
  }
  render() {
    const { components, ...props } = this.props

    return <MDXTag
             name="wrapper"
             
             components={components}><MDXTag name="h2" components={components} props={{"id":"roster-overview"}}>{`Roster Overview`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="ul" components={components}>
<MDXTag name="li" components={components} parentName="ul">{`HSF Affiliates is a real estate Franchisor having multiple real estate Franchisees (aka Companies, aka Brokers)`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="li" components={components} parentName="ul">{`Each Franchisee can have one or more Offices`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="li" components={components} parentName="ul">{`Each Office can have one or more Agents`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="li" components={components} parentName="ul">{`Roster data includes such things as the names, addresses, and contact info of Franchisees, Offices, and Agents`}</MDXTag>
</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="h2" components={components} props={{"id":"accessing-roster-data"}}>{`Accessing Roster Data`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="p" components={components}>{`The roster data inbox provides real-time updates of HSF Franchisees, Offices, Agents, Logos and Agent Profile Images.`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="p" components={components}>{`To request access for your application, please contact `}<MDXTag name="a" components={components} parentName="p" props={{"href":"mailto:michaelfortes@hsfranchise.com"}}>{`Michael Fortes`}</MDXTag></MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="h3" components={components} props={{"id":"production-data"}}>{`Production data`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="p" components={components}><MDXTag name="a" components={components} parentName="p" props={{"href":""}}>{`https://roster-data.ds.bhhsresource.com/inbox/`}</MDXTag></MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="h3" components={components} props={{"id":"devtest-data"}}>{`Dev/Test data`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="p" components={components}><MDXTag name="a" components={components} parentName="p" props={{"href":""}}>{`https://roster-data-test-schemav5.ds.bhhsresource.com/inbox/`}</MDXTag></MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="hr" components={components}></MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="h2" components={components} props={{"id":"roster-data-schemas"}}>{`Roster data schemas`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="p" components={components}>{`Follow the links before for schema definitions and examples `}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="ul" components={components}>
<MDXTag name="li" components={components} parentName="ul"><MDXTag name="a" components={components} parentName="li" props={{"href":"schema-real-estate-organization.md"}}>{`RealEstateOrganization`}</MDXTag></MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="li" components={components} parentName="ul"><MDXTag name="a" components={components} parentName="li" props={{"href":"schema-real-estate-office.md"}}>{`RealEstateOffice`}</MDXTag></MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="li" components={components} parentName="ul"><MDXTag name="a" components={components} parentName="li" props={{"href":"schema-real-estate-agent.md"}}>{`RealEstateAgent`}</MDXTag></MDXTag>
</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="h2" components={components} props={{"id":"franchise-relationship-model"}}>{`Franchise relationship model`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="p" components={components}>{`Franchise / Franchisee and Franchisee office relationships use parentOrganization and subOrganization properties.`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="pre" components={components}><MDXTag name="code" components={components} parentName="pre" props={{"className":"language-yaml"}}>{`# HSF Franchise
type: Organization
id: 'https://hsf.ds.bhhsresource.com/profile/card#me'
name: Berkshire Hathaway Home Services
subOrganization:
  # Franchisee
- type: Organization 
  id: 'https://ct301.ds.bhhsresource.com/profile/card#me'
  name: Berkshire Hathaway New England Properties
   
  parentOrganization:
  - id: 'https://hsf.ds.bhhsresource.com/profile/card#me'
 
  # Franchisee offices 
  subOrganization:
  - type: RealEstateOffice
    id: 'https://ct301-002.ds.bhhsresource.com/profile/card#me'
    
    parentOrganization:
    - type: Organziation
      id: 'https://ct301.ds.bhhsresource.com/profile/card#me'
    
`}</MDXTag></MDXTag>
           </MDXTag>
  }
}
